1
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:55,000
"Lost To You"

2
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,700
(Episode 12)

3
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:03,199
If the world is destined to collapse,

4
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:06,199
at least, in the ruins,

5
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:08,700
let me hold you tight.

6
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:22,500
Here.

7
00:01:22,791 --> 00:01:23,791
Drink it while it's hot.

8
00:01:26,083 --> 00:01:27,083
These past few days,

9
00:01:27,583 --> 00:01:29,083
you've barely eaten anything.

10
00:01:29,916 --> 00:01:30,916
Mom,

11
00:01:31,208 --> 00:01:32,208
I'm fine.

12
00:01:33,416 --> 00:01:34,416
Stop looking at it.

13
00:01:34,791 --> 00:01:35,791
Get some rest.

14
00:01:37,333 --> 00:01:38,750
It's not going anywhere.

15
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,000
Mom,

16
00:01:41,625 --> 00:01:42,705
have you ever regretted it?

17
00:01:44,458 --> 00:01:45,458
Regretted what?

18
00:01:46,500 --> 00:01:47,666
Regretted giving birth to me?

19
00:01:49,958 --> 00:01:51,208
I'm just a jinx.

20
00:01:51,541 --> 00:01:52,541
Nonsense.

21
00:01:53,458 --> 00:01:54,791
Don't say that.

22
00:01:55,416 --> 00:01:57,416
I've never believed in that nonsense.

23
00:01:58,208 --> 00:01:59,708
You are my best child,

24
00:02:00,375 --> 00:02:01,708
the apple of my eye.

25
00:02:06,458 --> 00:02:07,458
But...

26
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:10,375
But I killed Dad.

27
00:02:11,458 --> 00:02:12,666
Don't say that.

28
00:02:15,291 --> 00:02:17,041
Your dad did that to save you.

29
00:02:17,875 --> 00:02:19,208
It was because he loved you.

30
00:02:24,041 --> 00:02:25,416
He traded his own life

31
00:02:26,958 --> 00:02:28,791
so that you could live.

32
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,000
Xiao Yuan,

33
00:02:31,916 --> 00:02:33,291
it wasn't your fault.

34
00:02:34,375 --> 00:02:35,375
It was an accident.

35
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,875
Fate was just cruel.

36
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,000
Your dad,

37
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,250
he never regretted it.

38
00:02:48,375 --> 00:02:49,666
And neither do I.

39
00:02:50,208 --> 00:02:51,208
Mom,

40
00:02:51,333 --> 00:02:52,791
if you could turn back time,

41
00:02:55,083 --> 00:02:57,125
knowing Dad would leave so early

42
00:02:57,791 --> 00:02:58,958
and leave you to struggle

43
00:03:00,291 --> 00:03:01,750
to support this family alone,

44
00:03:04,041 --> 00:03:05,625
would you still choose to be with him?

45
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:09,750
Of course.

46
00:03:14,875 --> 00:03:16,833
The time I spent with your dad

47
00:03:18,583 --> 00:03:20,791
was the happiest

48
00:03:21,958 --> 00:03:23,416
and most peaceful time of my life.

49
00:03:26,125 --> 00:03:27,166
Even though it was short,

50
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,708
it was real.

51
00:03:36,541 --> 00:03:37,791
My only regret is

52
00:03:39,041 --> 00:03:40,958
that when he was still here,

53
00:03:44,458 --> 00:03:46,041
I couldn't make things easier

54
00:03:47,875 --> 00:03:49,166
and happier for him.

55
00:03:53,583 --> 00:03:54,583
Xiao Yuan,

56
00:03:56,541 --> 00:03:57,916
you and Xiao Nuo

57
00:03:58,875 --> 00:04:00,625
are the best proof

58
00:04:01,625 --> 00:04:03,500
of our love.

59
00:04:05,375 --> 00:04:08,000
No matter how hard it gets for me,

60
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:11,041
as long as you and Xiao Nuo are well,

61
00:04:14,125 --> 00:04:15,250
I have a purpose,

62
00:04:16,708 --> 00:04:18,028
and something to look forward to.

63
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,500
So,

64
00:04:27,625 --> 00:04:28,666
stop overthinking.

65
00:04:30,875 --> 00:04:31,875
Eat well,

66
00:04:32,291 --> 00:04:33,291
and live well.

67
00:04:34,083 --> 00:04:35,916
Your dad wouldn't
want to see you like this.

68
00:04:37,041 --> 00:04:38,041
Here,

69
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,000
drink it while it's hot.

70
00:05:33,625 --> 00:05:35,041
An obsession in the heart,

71
00:05:35,541 --> 00:05:36,916
be it a curse or a blessing,

72
00:05:37,208 --> 00:05:38,708
can change in an instant.

73
00:05:39,333 --> 00:05:40,916
Fortune and misfortune coexist,

74
00:05:41,458 --> 00:05:43,064
and things can always turn around.

75
00:05:43,089 --> 00:05:45,476
(“A sincere wish can reverse the tides of life."
Dec. 12th, afternoon, where the comet falls)

76
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,708
Whether it's true or not,

77
00:05:47,583 --> 00:05:48,750
and no matter the cost,

78
00:05:49,875 --> 00:05:50,875
Zhan Wang,

79
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:53,166
I will make sure you live.

80
00:05:58,041 --> 00:06:00,001
Zhan Wang, you must
transfer to another hospital.

81
00:06:01,166 --> 00:06:02,166
Get out.

82
00:06:02,625 --> 00:06:03,291
Don't be like this.

83
00:06:03,458 --> 00:06:04,858
We're doing this for your own good.

84
00:06:05,208 --> 00:06:06,208
Get out!

85
00:06:06,416 --> 00:06:07,416
Did you not hear me?

86
00:06:10,875 --> 00:06:11,541
Please step outside first.

87
00:06:11,625 --> 00:06:12,625
Okay.

88
00:06:16,416 --> 00:06:17,767
What are you throwing a tantrum for now?

89
00:06:17,791 --> 00:06:19,000
It's your body,

90
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:20,625
and your life.

91
00:06:21,041 --> 00:06:22,041
Where is he?

92
00:06:22,375 --> 00:06:23,541
Now is not the time for this.

93
00:06:24,291 --> 00:06:25,291
Take your medicine,

94
00:06:25,958 --> 00:06:26,666
and then transfer.

95
00:06:26,833 --> 00:06:27,833
If I don't see him,

96
00:06:28,875 --> 00:06:29,875
I'm not going anywhere.

97
00:06:30,875 --> 00:06:31,875
Anyway,

98
00:06:33,375 --> 00:06:34,666
there's no point in living.

99
00:06:35,083 --> 00:06:36,083
You ungrateful brat!

100
00:06:36,166 --> 00:06:37,806
I raised you all these years for nothing!

101
00:06:40,375 --> 00:06:41,375
Hit me!

102
00:06:42,333 --> 00:06:43,333
Go ahead, hit me!

103
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,500
Hit me right here.

104
00:06:46,291 --> 00:06:47,851
Just like you did to my second brother.

105
00:06:47,916 --> 00:06:48,916
Make me deaf,

106
00:06:49,125 --> 00:06:50,125
or beat me to death!

107
00:06:51,583 --> 00:06:53,875
How did I raise two
useless failures like you?

108
00:06:54,034 --> 00:06:55,076
We both take after you.

109
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:55,833
Shut up!

110
00:06:55,958 --> 00:06:57,017
You don't want me to say it,

111
00:06:57,041 --> 00:06:58,041
but I will.

112
00:06:59,458 --> 00:07:00,625
How old was I back then?

113
00:07:01,041 --> 00:07:02,041
Ten years old.

114
00:07:03,166 --> 00:07:04,666
You brought me back from Grandma's,

115
00:07:05,250 --> 00:07:07,041
and the first welcome ceremony I saw

116
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,750
was you almost beating
my second brother to death.

117
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,083
How did I end up with
such a filthy son like you?

118
00:07:22,375 --> 00:07:23,750
He brought it on himself.

119
00:07:24,666 --> 00:07:25,666
He refused to behave

120
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,625
and insisted on doing
those disgusting things.

121
00:07:29,625 --> 00:07:30,166
And another thing,

122
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:32,460
I brought you back to
keep you on the right path,

123
00:07:32,708 --> 00:07:34,458
not to follow those twisted ways.

124
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,320
What's the difference between us?

125
00:07:43,541 --> 00:07:45,421
Who is the man in those
photos in the darkroom?

126
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,470
Can you explain your relationship with him?

127
00:07:52,708 --> 00:07:53,708
Why am I like this?

128
00:07:54,375 --> 00:07:55,708
Don't you know why?

129
00:07:56,375 --> 00:07:57,375
Dad!

130
00:07:58,333 --> 00:07:59,708
You animal!

131
00:08:02,166 --> 00:08:03,166
Let go!

132
00:08:06,375 --> 00:08:07,615
He can't take any more of this.

133
00:08:10,291 --> 00:08:11,291
We had a deal.

134
00:08:12,875 --> 00:08:13,875
Leave him to me.

135
00:08:19,625 --> 00:08:20,625
Remember,

136
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:22,458
remember what you promised me.

137
00:08:29,916 --> 00:08:30,916
You're finally back.

138
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:34,110
I thought I'd never see you again.

139
00:08:35,291 --> 00:08:36,291
Brother Wang,

140
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:38,250
That won't happen.

141
00:08:38,458 --> 00:08:40,258
We still have a very
long future ahead of us.

142
00:08:44,333 --> 00:08:45,333
Actually,

143
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:48,833
your dad has accepted it.

144
00:08:54,125 --> 00:08:55,125
Really?

145
00:08:56,833 --> 00:08:57,833
Really.

146
00:08:58,916 --> 00:08:59,916
He promised me

147
00:09:00,916 --> 00:09:03,076
that as long as you go back
to Jingzhou for treatment,

148
00:09:03,416 --> 00:09:04,708
he will let us be together.

149
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,000
So,

150
00:09:07,458 --> 00:09:09,333
be good and go to Jingzhou for treatment,

151
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:11,750
okay?

152
00:09:15,291 --> 00:09:16,291
What about you?

153
00:09:16,625 --> 00:09:17,625
Come back with me.

154
00:09:18,875 --> 00:09:19,875
I have to stay.

155
00:09:21,833 --> 00:09:23,393
The college entrance exam is coming up,

156
00:09:24,083 --> 00:09:25,563
and my mom's noodle shop just opened.

157
00:09:27,166 --> 00:09:28,666
I can't leave them behind.

158
00:09:29,916 --> 00:09:31,041
A temporary separation

159
00:09:31,541 --> 00:09:32,916
is just for a better reunion.

160
00:09:34,250 --> 00:09:35,875
Go to Jingzhou and get treated.

161
00:09:36,208 --> 00:09:37,848
Once I get into a university in Jingzhou,

162
00:09:39,041 --> 00:09:40,041
we can be together.

163
00:09:41,500 --> 00:09:42,820
My dad isn't lying to you, is he?

164
00:09:44,958 --> 00:09:47,083
You won't... after I leave...

165
00:09:47,375 --> 00:09:48,375
I...

166
00:10:01,875 --> 00:10:02,875
I promise.

167
00:10:07,083 --> 00:10:08,083
Once my surgery is done,

168
00:10:09,041 --> 00:10:10,081
I'll come back right away.

169
00:10:12,041 --> 00:10:13,041
I'll wait for you.

170
00:10:18,375 --> 00:10:19,625
I'm not crippled.

171
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:21,791
Why do I need a wheelchair?

172
00:10:23,375 --> 00:10:25,295
You should move as
little as possible right now.

173
00:10:25,666 --> 00:10:26,666
Once you get there,

174
00:10:27,291 --> 00:10:28,458
listen to the doctors,

175
00:10:29,291 --> 00:10:30,833
eat and take your medicine on time,

176
00:10:31,458 --> 00:10:32,458
and don't be stubborn.

177
00:10:32,791 --> 00:10:34,111
Since you're so worried about me,

178
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:35,500
why don't

179
00:10:35,583 --> 00:10:36,583
we go together?

180
00:10:38,708 --> 00:10:39,750
I still have my exams.

181
00:10:41,041 --> 00:10:42,601
I'll come find you as soon as I'm done.

182
00:11:12,833 --> 00:11:13,833
This is for you.

183
00:11:14,541 --> 00:11:15,541
What's this?

184
00:11:15,875 --> 00:11:16,875
A gift for me?

185
00:11:18,541 --> 00:11:19,541
Don't look at it now.

186
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:21,875
You can only open it

187
00:11:22,125 --> 00:11:23,165
when you miss me terribly.

188
00:11:23,708 --> 00:11:24,708
What on earth is it?

189
00:11:25,125 --> 00:11:26,208
So mysterious.

190
00:11:27,875 --> 00:11:28,875
Promise me

191
00:11:29,916 --> 00:11:31,156
you'll focus on getting better.

192
00:11:31,541 --> 00:11:32,541
Of course.

193
00:11:33,916 --> 00:11:34,956
I want to get well quickly

194
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:36,875
so I can see you sooner.

195
00:11:38,458 --> 00:11:39,458
You must go to Jingzhou.

196
00:11:40,333 --> 00:11:41,333
I'll wait for you.

197
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:45,250
It's a promise.

198
00:11:50,791 --> 00:11:51,791
It's a promise.

199
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:56,083
Young Master, it's about time.

200
00:11:56,541 --> 00:11:57,916
You need a smooth ride to rest,

201
00:11:58,125 --> 00:11:59,205
so we can't drive too fast.

202
00:12:00,666 --> 00:12:01,666
Let's go.

203
00:12:04,166 --> 00:12:05,166
Xu Yuan.

204
00:12:05,375 --> 00:12:06,375
You can't lie to me.

205
00:12:07,208 --> 00:12:09,088
You promised you'd come
to Jingzhou to find me.

206
00:12:10,083 --> 00:12:11,723
Once I'm better, you'll come to Jingzhou.

207
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:13,470
Come over as soon as you finish your exams.

208
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,166
Do you hear me?

209
00:12:14,458 --> 00:12:15,458
Okay.

210
00:12:15,541 --> 00:12:16,541
Don't you dare lie to me.

211
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,000
You have to come soon.

212
00:12:22,708 --> 00:12:23,708
Xu Yuan.

213
00:12:29,041 --> 00:12:30,041
Xu Yuan.

214
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:32,291
Remember to call me when you miss me.

215
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:34,375
And reply when I text you.

216
00:12:34,541 --> 00:12:35,125
I will.

217
00:12:35,208 --> 00:12:36,488
Don't lie to me, okay? You hear?

218
00:12:37,041 --> 00:12:38,041
Remember to text me.

219
00:12:38,791 --> 00:12:39,791
Xu Yuan.

220
00:12:40,875 --> 00:12:41,875
Xu Yuan.

221
00:12:54,583 --> 00:12:55,863
Less than three hours left...

222
00:13:03,583 --> 00:13:05,263
The comet debris has suddenly accelerated.

223
00:13:05,458 --> 00:13:07,666
It is confirmed to impact
earlier than expected,

224
00:13:07,791 --> 00:13:08,583
at around 3:00 PM today,

225
00:13:08,791 --> 00:13:10,591
striking Hong Town and
the surrounding areas.

226
00:13:10,791 --> 00:13:11,833
All remaining residents

227
00:13:11,958 --> 00:13:13,918
must head to the designated
shelters immediately.

228
00:13:27,916 --> 00:13:29,076
Hurry up and get on the boat!

229
00:13:29,333 --> 00:13:30,333
What's happening?

230
00:13:30,833 --> 00:13:31,993
Why are the sirens going off?

231
00:13:32,708 --> 00:13:33,708
Take him away.

232
00:13:34,291 --> 00:13:36,291
I'm not leaving until you
tell me what's going on!

233
00:13:37,875 --> 00:13:38,875
Zhan Wang.

234
00:13:41,125 --> 00:13:42,125
Zhan Wang.

235
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:45,750
Zhan Wang.

236
00:13:46,458 --> 00:13:48,666
The news says the comet
is going to hit Hong Town.

237
00:13:48,916 --> 00:13:49,916
This afternoon.

238
00:13:49,958 --> 00:13:51,875
The entire town is being evacuated.

239
00:13:52,583 --> 00:13:54,333
I already sent Mom away.

240
00:13:54,541 --> 00:13:55,541
But my brother...

241
00:13:55,583 --> 00:13:56,125
Where is Xu Yuan?

242
00:13:56,250 --> 00:13:56,875
My brother...

243
00:13:57,083 --> 00:13:58,123
Where is Xu Yuan?

244
00:13:58,625 --> 00:14:00,708
He disappeared right
after he sent you away.

245
00:14:01,125 --> 00:14:02,500
We can't find him anywhere.

246
00:14:03,333 --> 00:14:05,125
We can't get in touch with him at all.

247
00:14:05,500 --> 00:14:06,125
Zhan Wang,

248
00:14:06,291 --> 00:14:07,208
is there any other way

249
00:14:07,291 --> 00:14:08,541
you can reach my brother?

250
00:14:08,833 --> 00:14:10,184
What do you mean you can't find him?

251
00:14:10,208 --> 00:14:11,208
Go look for him now!

252
00:14:11,666 --> 00:14:12,500
Go find him!

253
00:14:12,666 --> 00:14:13,666
Stop it.

254
00:14:14,208 --> 00:14:15,041
It's too dangerous right now.

255
00:14:15,083 --> 00:14:16,083
You must come with me.

256
00:14:16,125 --> 00:14:18,045
If it's dangerous, I need
to find him even more!

257
00:15:29,186 --> 00:15:33,059
(“A sincere wish can reverse the tides of life."
Dec. 12th, afternoon, where the comet falls)

258
00:15:35,041 --> 00:15:36,333
How could you be so foolish?

259
00:15:39,166 --> 00:15:40,291
How could you believe this?

260
00:15:50,041 --> 00:15:51,041
He didn't just disappear.

261
00:15:52,250 --> 00:15:53,541
He never planned on leaving!

262
00:15:58,333 --> 00:15:58,791
Dad!

263
00:15:59,166 --> 00:16:00,446
I'm going to find him right now.

264
00:16:01,416 --> 00:16:02,416
He's going to his death!

265
00:16:03,083 --> 00:16:04,333
If you want me to live,

266
00:16:04,791 --> 00:16:05,791
let me go right now!

267
00:16:06,125 --> 00:16:07,125
Ridiculous!

268
00:16:07,416 --> 00:16:08,496
What are you talking about?

269
00:16:08,708 --> 00:16:10,748
Look around. Do you think
you can even go back now?

270
00:16:11,375 --> 00:16:12,375
Then I'll run back!

271
00:16:12,791 --> 00:16:14,416
I can't let him die alone!

272
00:16:15,125 --> 00:16:16,125
Stop him!

273
00:16:18,625 --> 00:16:19,625
Let go of him!

274
00:16:22,708 --> 00:16:23,375
Go, Zhan Wang!

275
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:24,860
Now you're acting like a real man.

276
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,000
Dad,

277
00:16:27,916 --> 00:16:29,208
let him make his own choice.

278
00:16:46,416 --> 00:16:47,416
Uncle Zhan.

279
00:16:47,541 --> 00:16:48,541
Xu Nuo.

280
00:16:50,041 --> 00:16:51,041
Lin Xia.

281
00:16:51,166 --> 00:16:52,166
What are you doing here?

282
00:16:53,583 --> 00:16:54,976
My dad saw the evacuation of Hong Town

283
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,000
and knew you were here,

284
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,660
so he sent me to pick you up.

285
00:16:58,416 --> 00:16:59,416
But Xiao Wang ran off.

286
00:16:59,708 --> 00:17:01,188
We need to bring him back right away.

287
00:17:01,375 --> 00:17:01,791
Dad,

288
00:17:02,125 --> 00:17:03,125
stop trying to stop him.

289
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:06,083
Do you want to lose another life?

290
00:17:06,291 --> 00:17:07,291
You ungrateful brat!

291
00:17:07,416 --> 00:17:08,416
What are you saying?

292
00:17:08,916 --> 00:17:09,916
Uncle,

293
00:17:10,625 --> 00:17:12,785
wasn't the lesson of my
brother and Brother Xu enough?

294
00:17:15,375 --> 00:17:16,375
Sir,

295
00:17:17,625 --> 00:17:18,833
Um, Uncle,

296
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:21,500
Uncle Zhan,

297
00:17:21,541 --> 00:17:23,226
I've heard about what
happened to Brother Xu.

298
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:24,684
I don't think you did the right thing.

299
00:17:24,708 --> 00:17:27,268
Just because you're the father
doesn't mean you're always right.

300
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:29,500
You punk!

301
00:17:29,916 --> 00:17:30,916
Dad,

302
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,500
it's been so long.

303
00:17:35,375 --> 00:17:36,735
Now that things have come to this,

304
00:17:39,583 --> 00:17:40,583
let's have a talk.

305
00:17:54,458 --> 00:17:55,458
Zhan Wang,

306
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,333
you must find my brother.

307
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:00,000
And you both must stay safe.

308
00:18:01,791 --> 00:18:02,291
Don't worry.

309
00:18:02,791 --> 00:18:03,951
They will definitely be safe.

310
00:18:04,958 --> 00:18:05,958
Lin Xia,

311
00:18:06,166 --> 00:18:07,250
you're amazing.

312
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:09,083
How did you find us here?

313
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:10,750
Thanks to you.

314
00:18:13,125 --> 00:18:14,708
I didn't come back for them.

315
00:18:16,333 --> 00:18:18,250
Then... for me?

316
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:22,208
When I saw Hong Town was evacuating,

317
00:18:22,541 --> 00:18:23,621
I came back to pick you up.

318
00:18:24,166 --> 00:18:25,166
They were just a bonus.

319
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:29,750
Let's go.

320
00:18:32,416 --> 00:18:33,416
Dad,

321
00:18:34,083 --> 00:18:35,208
haven't you realized yet?

322
00:18:37,208 --> 00:18:38,208
Xiao Wang and I,

323
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:41,041
we've both grown up.

324
00:18:43,166 --> 00:18:44,708
We are braver than you ever were.

325
00:19:16,333 --> 00:19:17,333
Yes.

326
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,208
You are both braver than me.

327
00:19:23,125 --> 00:19:24,125
I forced my own fears

328
00:19:24,166 --> 00:19:25,458
onto you,

329
00:19:27,833 --> 00:19:29,833
thinking that holding you
back was protecting you.

330
00:19:31,625 --> 00:19:32,625
But I never realized

331
00:19:34,208 --> 00:19:35,666
it only ended up hurting you.

332
00:19:36,166 --> 00:19:37,166
Uncle,

333
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:38,250
since you've admitted

334
00:19:38,583 --> 00:19:39,708
we are braver than you,

335
00:19:39,958 --> 00:19:41,000
then you should accept us.

336
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:42,375
I promise

337
00:19:42,708 --> 00:19:44,392
I will take better care
of Zhan Xu than you did.

338
00:19:44,416 --> 00:19:46,583
And Xu Yuan will take
better care of Zhan Wang.

339
00:19:46,916 --> 00:19:47,625
The love we have

340
00:19:47,875 --> 00:19:48,995
is something you can't give.

341
00:20:03,583 --> 00:20:04,583
This path

342
00:20:05,833 --> 00:20:06,833
is very difficult.

343
00:20:07,958 --> 00:20:08,541
I love him.

344
00:20:08,958 --> 00:20:09,958
I love him.

345
00:20:11,166 --> 00:20:12,166
Trust us.

346
00:20:12,250 --> 00:20:13,250
Trust us.

347
00:20:23,458 --> 00:20:24,458
Xu Yuan, wait for me.

348
00:20:25,166 --> 00:20:26,166
You must stay safe.

349
00:20:29,958 --> 00:20:30,958
Zhan Wang.

350
00:20:31,291 --> 00:20:32,500
I will make sure you're safe.

351
00:20:37,996 --> 00:20:38,996
Fuck!

352
00:20:39,250 --> 00:20:40,250
The battery died.

353
00:20:54,916 --> 00:20:55,916
Xu Yuan,

354
00:20:56,041 --> 00:20:56,541
wait for me.

355
00:20:56,958 --> 00:20:57,958
You must wait for me.

356
00:20:58,500 --> 00:20:59,500
Don't do anything stupid.

357
00:21:00,041 --> 00:21:01,641
We promised to watch the comet together,

358
00:21:01,958 --> 00:21:02,958
but not like this.

359
00:21:03,375 --> 00:21:04,375
Not like this.

360
00:21:12,583 --> 00:21:14,416
Young man, don't run in there!

361
00:21:16,416 --> 00:21:17,500
Don't go that way!

362
00:21:17,583 --> 00:21:19,458
That's the impact zone, kid!

363
00:21:32,041 --> 00:21:33,041
Get in.

364
00:21:33,416 --> 00:21:34,416
I'm not going with you.

365
00:21:35,625 --> 00:21:37,225
Riding is faster than running, isn't it?

366
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:38,660
Aren't you going to find him?

367
00:21:40,333 --> 00:21:41,853
If we don't go now, it'll be too late!

368
00:21:56,458 --> 00:21:57,458
I need to hurry.

369
00:22:12,916 --> 00:22:14,036
How did you find this place?

370
00:22:16,125 --> 00:22:18,083
I've lived here much longer than you.

371
00:22:18,875 --> 00:22:20,715
The mountain paths and
backroads of Hong Town,

372
00:22:20,875 --> 00:22:22,875
which ones are passable,
which ones are shortcuts,

373
00:22:22,916 --> 00:22:24,356
I know them better than you do, kid.

374
00:22:27,041 --> 00:22:28,041
Why?

375
00:22:28,458 --> 00:22:29,458
What?

376
00:22:30,458 --> 00:22:31,458
Why are you helping me?

377
00:22:34,375 --> 00:22:37,083
I used to think you were
just young and impulsive,

378
00:22:37,666 --> 00:22:38,708
not knowing what love is,

379
00:22:39,083 --> 00:22:40,123
or what responsibility is.

380
00:22:41,666 --> 00:22:42,666
But now,

381
00:22:44,166 --> 00:22:46,458
I realize I was the one
who never truly understood.

382
00:22:50,333 --> 00:22:51,750
What's the use of saying this now?

383
00:22:52,916 --> 00:22:53,916
I don't even know

384
00:22:54,833 --> 00:22:55,851
how much longer I have to live.

385
00:22:55,875 --> 00:22:56,875
You have to live.

386
00:22:59,666 --> 00:23:01,750
You and Xu Yuan have
to survive this together.

387
00:23:02,333 --> 00:23:04,958
Both of you must stay alive.

388
00:23:05,958 --> 00:23:06,958
The road ahead,

389
00:23:07,833 --> 00:23:08,953
you'll choose it yourselves.

390
00:23:18,750 --> 00:23:19,830
This is as far as I can go.

391
00:23:19,875 --> 00:23:20,875
He's right here.

392
00:23:21,083 --> 00:23:22,500
Xiao Wang, stay safe.

393
00:23:22,833 --> 00:23:24,273
Make sure you bring him back safely.

394
00:24:52,791 --> 00:24:53,791
Xu Yuan,

395
00:24:55,958 --> 00:24:56,958
wait for me.

396
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,000
This is the place.

397
00:25:56,791 --> 00:25:58,708
I, Zhan Wang, just want to see

398
00:25:59,625 --> 00:26:00,750
how unlucky one can get

399
00:26:02,375 --> 00:26:03,500
by being Xu Yuan's friend.

400
00:26:05,125 --> 00:26:05,875
What are you doing?

401
00:26:06,041 --> 00:26:06,541
Bian Ye.

402
00:26:06,791 --> 00:26:08,351
Bullying a classmate in broad daylight?

403
00:26:08,666 --> 00:26:09,809
You're the ones who deserve to be beaten!

404
00:26:09,833 --> 00:26:11,333
Every time before art class,

405
00:26:11,916 --> 00:26:12,708
he organizes everything.

406
00:26:12,833 --> 00:26:14,166
You all take it for granted,

407
00:26:14,375 --> 00:26:16,215
and blame him the moment
something goes wrong.

408
00:26:16,875 --> 00:26:17,875
Jinx.

409
00:26:17,916 --> 00:26:18,916
Is he really a jinx,

410
00:26:18,958 --> 00:26:20,434
or are you just used to shifting the blame

411
00:26:20,458 --> 00:26:22,166
onto a classmate who won't talk back?

412
00:26:26,750 --> 00:26:27,750
Watch out.

413
00:26:35,416 --> 00:26:36,416
You idiot.

414
00:26:37,375 --> 00:26:38,684
Who asked you to shield me like that?

415
00:26:38,708 --> 00:26:40,188
And get yourself hurt in the process?

416
00:26:40,625 --> 00:26:41,745
Your head is more important.

417
00:26:43,833 --> 00:26:44,833
What are you doing?

418
00:26:45,708 --> 00:26:46,750
Do you have any mints?

419
00:26:47,375 --> 00:26:48,375
I want one.

420
00:26:53,708 --> 00:26:54,708
Thanks.

421
00:26:54,750 --> 00:26:56,030
The people who matter most to me

422
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:57,583
are all in this room.

423
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:03,000
Does that include me?

424
00:27:03,625 --> 00:27:04,625
What if...

425
00:27:05,375 --> 00:27:06,791
What if I end up hurting you too?

426
00:27:07,458 --> 00:27:08,708
It was never your fault.

427
00:27:09,875 --> 00:27:10,875
Besides,

428
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:12,916
I'm tough.

429
00:27:13,791 --> 00:27:14,791
I can take a beating.

430
00:27:20,416 --> 00:27:22,000
I'm also a monster in my dad's eyes.

431
00:27:24,791 --> 00:27:25,791
For liking men.

432
00:27:32,708 --> 00:27:34,788
It's because you never
liked men in the first place.

433
00:27:35,333 --> 00:27:36,333
It was me.

434
00:27:37,625 --> 00:27:38,958
I was the one who went crazy.

435
00:27:40,166 --> 00:27:41,166
Zhan Wang.

436
00:27:42,625 --> 00:27:43,625
Zhan Wang.

437
00:27:44,958 --> 00:27:45,958
I like you.

438
00:27:46,291 --> 00:27:47,291
Xiao Yuan-yuan.

439
00:27:48,291 --> 00:27:49,291
I'm here.

440
00:28:05,416 --> 00:28:07,000
All those times you had headaches,

441
00:28:07,166 --> 00:28:08,351
taking medicine over and over,

442
00:28:08,375 --> 00:28:09,855
and feeling unwell again and again...

443
00:28:11,416 --> 00:28:12,833
Why didn't you tell me?

444
00:28:13,750 --> 00:28:14,750
Or is it...

445
00:28:15,333 --> 00:28:17,614
Or did you just never think
about having a future with me?

446
00:28:17,666 --> 00:28:18,666
No.

447
00:28:19,583 --> 00:28:20,743
I did think about our future.

448
00:28:22,958 --> 00:28:23,958
But I was afraid...

449
00:28:26,375 --> 00:28:27,815
that I might not have a future left.

450
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:31,000
Xu Yuan.

451
00:28:31,250 --> 00:28:32,875
I wish to offer all my luck,

452
00:28:33,125 --> 00:28:34,125
my lifespan,

453
00:28:34,458 --> 00:28:35,458
and everything I have,

454
00:28:36,166 --> 00:28:39,250
in exchange for Zhan Wang's
lifelong health and safety.

455
00:28:39,375 --> 00:28:40,695
Free from illness and misfortune.

456
00:28:41,375 --> 00:28:42,375
Please.

457
00:28:46,625 --> 00:28:47,625
Xu Yuan.

458
00:28:48,708 --> 00:28:49,333
My boyfriend,

459
00:28:49,541 --> 00:28:50,125
Zhan Wang.

460
00:28:50,250 --> 00:28:52,040
Do you have any idea what
nonsense you're talking?

461
00:28:52,041 --> 00:28:53,375
This is my own choice.

462
00:28:53,416 --> 00:28:54,416
I'm not wrong.

463
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,000
Zhan Wang.

464
00:28:56,958 --> 00:28:58,278
I know you miss Granny very much,

465
00:28:59,125 --> 00:29:00,708
but I won't let you go see her so soon.

466
00:29:02,250 --> 00:29:03,370
I absolutely won't allow it.

467
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,041
Ten years from now,

468
00:29:06,583 --> 00:29:09,041
I still want to be with Zhan Wang.

469
00:29:12,208 --> 00:29:13,333
Ten years from now,

470
00:29:14,833 --> 00:29:16,916
I still want to be with Xu Yuan.

471
00:29:18,416 --> 00:29:21,750
We'll be together forever.

472
00:29:44,458 --> 00:29:45,458
Xu Yuan.

473
00:29:48,916 --> 00:29:49,916
Xu Yuan.

474
00:30:55,541 --> 00:30:56,541
Get on.

475
00:30:57,291 --> 00:30:58,291
This bike is for you.

476
00:30:58,833 --> 00:31:00,473
Aren't you helping your mom deliver food?

477
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:01,500
Running is too slow.

478
00:31:02,333 --> 00:31:04,093
This is faster. You can
deliver more orders.

479
00:31:04,750 --> 00:31:05,750
I don't want it.

480
00:31:07,833 --> 00:31:08,875
It's not for free.

481
00:31:09,041 --> 00:31:10,041
The condition is...

482
00:31:10,208 --> 00:31:12,448
you have to give me a ride
to and from school every day.

483
00:31:13,125 --> 00:31:14,666
I don't want to walk every day.

484
00:31:14,916 --> 00:31:15,916
It's exhausting.

485
00:31:15,958 --> 00:31:16,958
No way.

486
00:31:17,375 --> 00:31:18,495
Riding with me is dangerous.

487
00:31:20,541 --> 00:31:21,541
Let's give it a try.

488
00:31:22,583 --> 00:31:24,083
I've been through a lot.

489
00:31:24,208 --> 00:31:26,291
I'm not afraid of your jinx status.

490
00:31:27,083 --> 00:31:27,583
Get on.

491
00:31:27,958 --> 00:31:29,678
Your mom already sent me the order numbers.

492
00:31:29,833 --> 00:31:30,993
Let's deliver the food first.

493
00:32:18,791 --> 00:32:19,291
This is it.

494
00:32:19,625 --> 00:32:20,625
The white house.

495
00:32:21,416 --> 00:32:23,208
No. 108 Xingfu [Happiness] Road.

496
00:32:35,166 --> 00:32:36,166
Here's your delivery.

497
00:32:39,208 --> 00:32:40,041
How unlucky!

498
00:32:40,166 --> 00:32:42,017
Running into a jinx like you
always brings me bad luck.

499
00:32:42,041 --> 00:32:42,541
I don't want the noodles anymore.

500
00:32:42,666 --> 00:32:43,666
Take them away.

501
00:32:49,625 --> 00:32:50,666
This stupid flowerpot

502
00:32:51,250 --> 00:32:52,530
was clearly not placed properly.

503
00:32:53,041 --> 00:32:54,601
Blaming the delivery instead of herself.

504
00:32:54,625 --> 00:32:55,625
What was she thinking?

505
00:32:55,833 --> 00:32:56,833
If she won't eat it,

506
00:32:57,041 --> 00:32:58,041
I will.

507
00:32:59,583 --> 00:33:00,583
Forget it.

508
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,160
It's someone's unwanted food.

509
00:33:02,208 --> 00:33:04,333
Who says eating your
deliveries brings bad luck?

510
00:33:04,458 --> 00:33:05,658
I'm going to prove them wrong.

511
00:33:22,583 --> 00:33:23,583
Delicious!

512
00:33:24,125 --> 00:33:25,125
Now,

513
00:33:25,833 --> 00:33:26,833
all we need is a drink.

514
00:33:28,708 --> 00:33:29,726
That bottle I gave you this morning,

515
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:30,750
did you drink it?

516
00:33:32,166 --> 00:33:33,286
I don't usually drink sodas.

517
00:33:34,166 --> 00:33:35,166
It's in my bag.

518
00:33:45,228 --> 00:33:46,588
Hot damn.

519
00:33:49,791 --> 00:33:50,791
See?

520
00:33:51,166 --> 00:33:52,886
(Win another bottle)
Who says you're a jinx?

521
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,333
You're clearly my lucky star.

522
00:33:56,458 --> 00:33:57,458
Are you full?

523
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:59,510
We still have a few
more deliveries to make.

524
00:34:01,125 --> 00:34:01,458
Let's go.

525
00:34:01,875 --> 00:34:02,875
Let's go.

526
00:34:15,541 --> 00:34:16,791
Brother, you're back.

527
00:34:17,416 --> 00:34:18,416
Look, look!

528
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,500
This.

529
00:34:21,250 --> 00:34:23,791
Drink companies are so creative these days.

530
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:26,500
What is this?

531
00:34:26,541 --> 00:34:27,541
Customized bottle caps.

532
00:34:27,916 --> 00:34:28,750
My classmate said

533
00:34:28,791 --> 00:34:30,000
a boy gave her a drink,

534
00:34:30,250 --> 00:34:32,041
and the cap had "I
like you" engraved on it.

535
00:34:32,291 --> 00:34:33,291
So romantic!

536
00:34:34,337 --> 00:34:37,044
(I like you.)

537
00:34:42,416 --> 00:34:43,416
Lame.

538
00:34:43,875 --> 00:34:44,875
It's all a gimmick.

539
00:34:45,333 --> 00:34:46,333
No, it's not!

540
00:34:46,750 --> 00:34:47,910
It's the thought that counts.

541
00:34:48,333 --> 00:34:50,750
This is way more precious
than winning any lottery.

542
00:34:57,666 --> 00:34:58,666
I'm heading inside.

543
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:07,500
(Win another bottle)

544
00:35:08,833 --> 00:35:10,083
It really was customized.

545
00:35:10,416 --> 00:35:11,416
I knew it.

546
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:12,740
How could anyone be that lucky?
